        "id": 5395
      },
      "writtenOn": "2021-06-17T13:19:00Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Please describe this param - IIUC, this allows people to specify the language. Should we consider making this required, so there\u0027s less \"undefined\" behavior?\n\nI recall there being situations where setting the language to different settings can cause breaking or spaces or graphemes to be different - I think it would be illustrative to provide at least one motivating case here for that.",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 70,
        "startChar": 22,
        "endLine": 70,
        "endChar": 27
      },
      "revId": "71c2789454b6b8954491b0944d490d44b359a41a",
